docs.text:
To create/ edit purchase orders, manage deliveries from suppliers to warehouses and return items from warehouses to suppliers, go to  Purchase Management > Purchase Order > Purchase Order . The Manage Purchase Orders page contains information related to all POs including  Reference Number, Date of the PO, Supplier, Ordered Qty, Received Qty, Billed Qty, Total Paid, Grand Total inclusive Tax  (i.e. the total value of the PO) and  Status .    There are 3 types of Status indicating to which stage the PO has been processed:
-  Pending : when you have input General Information and prepared product list;
-  Processing : when you click the Confirm Purchase Order button;
-  Completed : when you click the Complete PO button.  Click on view a PO to see more details of the PO and you can continue editing the PO.
